General.Name: Metal Hawk Ltd
General.Description: Metal Hawk Limited engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral resource projects in Western Australia. It explores for gold and nickel sulphide deposits. The company's properties include the Kanowna East, Emu Lake, Fraser South, and Blair North and Clinker Hill projects. Metal Hawk Limited was incorporated in 2018 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
